  "id": "RAW_53ff0f72",
  "title": "【早阅】OpenSpec：全新工具包告别 Vibe 编码！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651277814&idx=1&sn=4e3f0dbced653507f7eefdcbac58f84a",
  "date": "2025-11-03 00:03:00",
  "author": "前端早读课",
  "siteName": "前端早读课",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=19fcb6f6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FmeG6Vo0MeviaYC9a2NY1PPicXv1ic3rW0k4GLrYzWPLCBTbOS9rDkWc8TVG3LP8DsE2BTf0hKAuWBNKncFRF07ksw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">别再浪费时间在模糊的 “凭感觉写代码” 上了！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:0px !important;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这篇完整的教程中，我们将深入讲解 OpenSpec —— 一款能够彻底改变 AI 编码助手工作方式的新工具包。将学会如何创建结构化、以规范为驱动（spec-driven）的项目，让开发过程更可审查、可预测，效率比传统的 “凭感觉写代码” 高出 100 倍。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">规格驱动开发的局限性与 OpenSpec 的登场</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">GitHub Spec Kit 作为一项开源工具包，旨在通过规格驱动开发的方法论，显著提升代码质量和开发效率。其核心优势在于允许 AI 代理直接聚焦于可执行的规范，从而生成实际可运行的实现，而非仅仅是听起来合理但无法运行的 “氛围代码”。然而，Spec Kit 最理想的应用场景是全新的、从零开始的项目开发。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651277763&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=238e98aaf698e4d4c02de0aa4f3e37ca&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3605期】通过规范驱动开发提升你的 AI 开发水平\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3605期】通过规范驱动开发提升你的 AI 开发水平</a></span></p>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">现有代码库演进的挑战</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">一旦代码库开始演进，跨规范管理更新和变更就会变得非常混乱，这使得 Spec Kit 不适合持续的开发流程。OpenSpec 应运而生，它建立在规格驱动开发的基础上，旨在使人类和 AI 编码助手在编写任何代码之前就对构建内容达成一致。OpenSpec 的优势在于它更加轻量化，无需 API 密钥，并确保开发意图在实现代码前被锁定，提供更具确定性和可审查的结果。</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;padding-left:2em;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">比 Spec Kit 更轻量且易于操作。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">无需依赖 API 密钥进行操作。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">保证开发意图在实现前被锁定。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">提供更具确定性、更易于审查的输出结果。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenSpec 的核心优势与工具对比</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503794152\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=38b2aa6d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FmeG6Vo0Mevj7RalGebTqmSwMibIMpJYMJ86Iz1WDicXJZlBqvHYoYbDEt4uuNmx0VOnCAoG5DLyE0Roz1csttQmg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenSpec 在处理演进中的功能方面表现更优越，它通过为当前规范和拟议更改设置独立的文件夹，实现了当前状态与提议更新的清晰分离。这与 Curo 工具包将所有更新集中在一个地方以便于跟踪的做法形成了对比。OpenSpec 的核心目标是为修改现有系统带来更清晰的结构和控制力。</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(221, 221, 221);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它将为修改现有系统带来更清晰的结构，干净地分离您当前的真实情况和提议的更新。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">与无规范工具的差异</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">与不采用任何规格驱动工具包的情况相比，OpenSpec 能够确保产生更可预测、事先商定的输出结果，而不是依赖于自然提示生成的模糊代码。此外，OpenSpec 得到了 Cloud Code、Cursor、Open Code、Kilo Code、CodeEx 等多种工具的支持，后续还将集成更多工具，例如 Gemini CLI。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651277468&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=555fad29ddf6adaed65dd6b2032b9ec7&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3591期】GitHub Spec-Kit：规范驱动开发走在正确的方向上 - 严谨、渐进式的 Vibe Coding\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3591期】GitHub Spec-Kit：规范驱动开发走在正确的方向上 - 严谨、渐进式的 Vibe Coding</a></span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Zapier 在 AI 工具浪潮中的地位</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503794153\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3e750de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FmeG6Vo0Mevj7RalGebTqmSwMibIMpJYMJVoYggtpGFOIEoxxwa4AYZWNTm6FS1ozPwuYEqSPaMLSk5kcOSkmblw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">尽管新的 AI 工具不断涌现，人们常错误地认为 Zapier 已经过时。实际上，Zapier 从未像现在这样充满活力。例如，新推出的 Agent Kit 主要关注答案优化而非工作流程编排，它帮助聊天机器人更好地思考，但 Zapier 则负责跨越 8000 多个应用进行确定性的操作编排，这一点是其核心竞争力所在。</span></p>\n  <table style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-spacing:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;width:360px;margin-bottom:16px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <thead>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">特性</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Zapier</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Agent Kit / 其他工具</span></p>\n     </th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">核心功能</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">工作流程编排与跨应用自动化</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">答案优化 / 思考增强</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">可靠性</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">确定性可靠性</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">倾向于生成 / 建议</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Zapier 甚至能与 OpenAI 的新 MCP 兼容，允许通过 ChatGPT 路由答案并用 Zapier 自动化结果。Zapier 通过 Cobot 功能，现在允许用户用自然语言描述需求，即可构建完整的生产级工作流程。新的 Opus Clip 集成还进一步扩展了其能力，可自动化视频内容再利用流程，显示出其持续的创新和领先地位。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenSpec 的安装与项目初始化配置</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">要开始使用 OpenSpec，首先需要确保安装了最新版本的 Node.js，然后通过 npm 命令全局安装 OpenSpec 工具包。安装完成后，运行 openspec version 命令可以验证安装是否成功。此后，即可在目标项目目录中执行初始化命令，为 AI 驱动的开发流程做好准备。</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;padding-left:2em;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">确保 Node.js 版本是最新的。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">使用 npm install 命令进行全局安装。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">运行 openspec version 验证安装状态。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">在项目目录中运行 openspec initialize 进行设置。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">配置首选 AI 助手</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">初始化过程会提示配置所选的 AI 助手，如 GitHub Copilot、Kilo Code 或 Cloud Code。选择后，OpenSpec 会自动生成一个 agents.md 文件，其中包含针对特定 AI 代理的自定义斜杠命令和工具特定指令。该文件随后会被传递给编码代理，并与项目文件关联起来，确保 AI 理解当前项目的上下文和要求。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">利用 OpenSpec 生成和实施功能更新</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503794155\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=21421581&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FmeG6Vo0Mevj7RalGebTqmSwMibIMpJYMJCHKvpRtmnct3UA5uhbVIXLyn8VmV84t8YSYH5sXSlUWV8smU6GmJtw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">工作流程的第一步是填充项目上下文。这涉及复制 OpenSpec 提供的自然提示，并将其发送给选定的 AI 代理（例如 Kilo Code），指示它阅读项目 MD 文件并根据技术栈填充必要细节。代理随后会更新 project.md 文件，提供关于 AI 检测工具的全面信息，为后续开发奠定基础。</span></p>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">创建功能变更提案</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来，需要向 OpenSpec 提供所需遵循的所有功能。通过复制特定提示并添加功能描述，例如请求创建 AI 检测工具的 OpenSpec 变更提案。在 project.md 文件中，OpenSpec 会写入架构模式、状态管理、测试策略等必要细节，以确保应用程序的效率和质量。</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(221, 221, 221);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个设计 MD 已经生成了所有不同的任务列表，您可以审阅所有内容，看看是否要继续执行。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">随后，将功能请求发送给 Kilo Code 执行。Kilo Code 之所以被选用，是因为它能理解并自主处理 OpenSpec 生成的各种命令和任务，同时保持用户的知情权。在生成提案的详细信息后，用户可以审查设计 MD 和任务列表等提案文件，并可移除不希望执行的部分，从而保持对开发流程的完全控制。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">成本效益与最终实现效果展示</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503794156\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eb2e5c3b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FmeG6Vo0Mevj7RalGebTqmSwMibIMpJYMJQm5ia6J8xeg8IicWh4hgSC9EytuC7xPgVPkVlEbgNIXNcXKickNT4FcJg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后一步是执行变更，即指示 AI 代理根据 OpenSpec 提案实现 AI 检测工具。在实施过程中，明确指示代理不要添加提案中未指定的额外功能。执行任务时，可以运行 openspec view 命令来监控进度，了解当前正在处理的任务数量，确保流程透明化。</span></p>\n  <table style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-spacing:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;width:360px;margin-bottom:16px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <thead>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">工具</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">成本 / 时间</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">结果</span></p>\n     </th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">OpenSpec + Kilo Code</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">约 0.48 美元 (不含计划费用)</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">功能齐全的 AI 检测工具</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Spec Kit (参考)</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">约 5 美元 (生成计划)</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">提议计划</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最终，AI 检测工具生成完毕。通过输入 AI 生成的故事文本进行分析，工具能自信地识别出这是 AI 检测内容，并提供关于困惑度（Perplexity）和突发性（Burstiness）等指标的详细分析。所有这些都是由 Kilo Code 驱动 OpenSpec 生成的，总成本仅为约 2 美元（包含计划费用）。虽然前端界面（使用 Cloud Sonic 4.5）可能不美观，但输出的质量和功能的实现是完全符合预期的，展示了 OpenSpec 的强大能力。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">问题</span></h4>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenSpec 与 GitHub Spec Kit 的主要区别是什么？</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Spec Kit 最适合全新项目，而 OpenSpec 则专为修改和演进现有系统而设计，能更优雅地处理规范的更新和变更，避免了管理混乱。</span></p>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenSpec 如何确保 AI 生成的代码质量和准确性？</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenSpec 通过在实现代码之前锁定开发者的意图，确保 AI 代理专注于可执行的规范，从而提供更具确定性和可审查的结果，避免了模糊的猜测。</span></p>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用 OpenSpec 进行功能开发的大致成本是多少？</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频演示中，使用 OpenSpec 和 Kilo Code 生成一个完整的 AI 检测工具，总成本仅花费了约 0.48 美元（不含计划费用），远低于其他工具的成本。</span></p>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么说 Zapier 在新的 AI 工具浪潮中依然重要？</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Zapier 的核心价值在于其工作流程编排能力，能够跨越 8000 多个应用进行确定性的操作执行，这是许多专注于答案优化的新 AI 工具所不具备的。</span></p>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenSpec 初始化后会生成哪些关键文件？</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">初始化后会生成 agents.md 文件，用于配置特定 AI 助手的自定义命令和指令，以及更新 project.md 文件，包含关于项目和技术栈的全面细节。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">早读洞察</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">1、OpenSpec 解决现有项目更新的规范管理难题：相比 Spec Kit 不适合持续开发，OpenSpec 专为修改现有系统而设计，能干净地分离当前事实与拟议更新，提升了代码演进的管理效率。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">2、确保意图锁定，实现确定性的 AI 代码生成: OpenSpec 确保在实现代码前锁定开发者的意图，提供可审查的结果，避免了 AI 的猜测性输出，从而带来更可靠的开发体验。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">3、结构化管理提案、任务和规范更新：该工具通过结构化管理，使范围变更具有可审计性和透明度，通过 proposals、tasks 等机制提升了协作的清晰度。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">4、OpenSpec 支持多种主流 AI 编码助手集成：该工具兼容 Cloud Code、Cursor、Kilo Code 等多种 AI 助手，并能自动配置特定指令，实现无缝集成。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">5、实施新功能开发成本显著降低：演示显示，使用 OpenSpec 和 Kilo Code 生成完整项目仅花费约 0.48 美元，与依赖 Spec Kit 的工具相比，成本效益极高。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">6、Zapier 在 AI 编排领域仍保持核心地位：尽管有新的 AI 工具出现，Zapier 凭借其跨 8000 多个应用的确定性编排能力，依然是自动化领域的领导者，而非被取代。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:0px !important;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">原文：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHkdrO6IExM\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHkdrO6IExM</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "OpenSpec 是一款全新的规范驱动 AI 编码工具包，旨在解决现有代码库演进中的规范管理难题，提升 AI 辅助开发的确定性和效率。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "OpenSpec 是一款全新的规范驱动 AI 编码工具包，旨在解决现有代码库演进中的规范管理难题，提升 AI 辅助开发的确定性和效率。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了 OpenSpec，一个专为 AI 编码助手设计的全新工具包，旨在通过规范驱动开发（spec-driven）彻底改变 AI 辅助编码方式。它解决了 GitHub Spec Kit 在处理现有代码库演进时面临的规范管理混乱问题，通过将当前状态与提议更新清晰分离，使开发过程更可审查、可预测。OpenSpec 的优势在于其轻量化、无需 API 密钥，并能确保开发意图在代码实现前被锁定，从而生成高质量、可运行的代码，而非模糊的“氛围代码”。文章对比了 OpenSpec 与无规范工具的差异，强调其能产生更可预测的输出。同时，文章也提及了 Zapier 在 AI 工具浪潮中的独特价值，即其强大的工作流程编排能力。最后，文章提供了 OpenSpec 的安装、项目初始化、AI 助手配置以及功能更新生成与实施的详细步骤，并通过一个 AI 检测工具的开发案例，展示了 OpenSpec 与 Kilo Code 结合的显著成本效益和实现效果。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "OpenSpec 解决现有代码库演进中规范管理的痛点，提升 AI 辅助开发的确定性。",
      "explanation": "相比 Spec Kit 更适用于全新项目，OpenSpec 专为修改现有系统设计，通过清晰分离当前状态和提议更新，确保开发意图被锁定，避免 AI 生成模糊代码。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OpenSpec 通过结构化流程，实现 AI 编码助手生成高质量、可审查的代码。",
      "explanation": "它支持多种主流 AI 编码助手，自动化配置指令，并提供项目上下文填充、功能变更提案创建及执行等步骤，确保开发结果符合预期。"
    },
